The paper deals with wireless caching and physical layer security in cellular networks, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The focus on video streaming suggests a connection to multimedia (cs.MM), while the emphasis on security aligns with the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the optimization problem formulation and solution methods suggest a connection to control systems (cs.SY).
